Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么啊 这种奇怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是垃圾场附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的体温对止住眼泪很有效 是妈妈告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个槛 我一定要越过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好上学的话 会留级的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也差不了多少吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那是在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近黑之骑士团的活动变得活跃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是技术部的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 人手不足啊… 哪里都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 偶尔也来我家吃顿饭怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今晚的话没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样好吗 会不会给你添麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 鲁鲁修!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道会长要去相亲的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你知道为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你的话 你会哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑给你看!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦 我也不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候不要做这种纯真的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯真?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样子就是所谓的纯真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么吃饭的事 我就先去告诉娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还有课啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 只是先去告诉她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的烦恼 就这样置之不理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的课不是从第二节开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到相亲的话 一般会选在酒店或餐厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 我听说罗伊德伯爵是个非常『独特』的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『独特』 还真是不错的形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然准备迎娶被剥夺爵位、正在衰败的阿斯福德家的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爵位什么的无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用慢慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就暂且搁置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉 朱雀他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是叫我待在这里不准动…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太大意了啊 鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在C.C.不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟Geass无效的对手很麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事之后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不回敬你上次的大礼 我实在无法平静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该在500米以内吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间限制是5小时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这是我和你之间的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果使用警察这一棋子就要出局哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想好像上次那样被枪击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 布里塔尼亚的医学还真是厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托它的福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的Geass不应是『开枪』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而应该是『杀了他』才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你的天真 你妹妹才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入险境了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入危机了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落入绝境了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉与此无关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为游戏来说 不觉得太卑鄙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想借此令哥哥伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 午休了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉和鲁鲁修吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 所以会长说要暂时配合他们两个玩『陌生人游戏』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样了啊 相亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 比起那个 还是莎莉和鲁鲁修…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随他们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是日常的夫妻吵架罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 可是你不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 这和我可没有关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是那小子想越线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越线?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修他空有理论知识 但实战很弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实战?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经验不足啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:08:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经验?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:08:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟 为什么你总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和莎莉怎样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不送她个礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 上课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午还不去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 晚上的事 等会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在玩赌博游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你到处找都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间限制给你延长一小时哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看穿我这边焦头烂额了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了读取我的思考
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是在我500米以内的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是娜娜莉出了什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭马上就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:10:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭…  你出去买东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  只是用现成的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是害怕外面的布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想起什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你还有伤在身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果合你口味就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掳走娜娜莉的是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是… 布里塔尼亚的皇族?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 和我们的身份没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是某个想占有女孩子的小鬼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被威胁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被调查的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的身份也许会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能向军方或警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们自己想办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这真的和赌博什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 有什么线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有照片 还有他在附近能够监视我的距离以内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 似乎有水流淌的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,循环系统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地底的设施吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是平常的你 应该会立刻察觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据被篡改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好破坏门锁系统了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是违反校规吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后修好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我来破坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 已经打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会太过熟练了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里部分的管理是由学生会负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都有利用这个溜到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 偶尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视摄像机联动着机关枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种系统的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应延迟时间大约为0.05秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说无法从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回到上面把系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉在等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 朱雀也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 现在马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木擅自跟来这事 我就原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个好好努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会把炸弹拆除的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和鲁鲁修联手 没有做不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摆感应炸弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让其不停运动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的缆线一直给它提供能量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果受到其它外力影响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 应该假设移动娜娜莉的话也会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能估计爆炸影响范围吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半径500米以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 超出毛的Geass有效范围
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道拆除的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理论上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要切断连接引爆装置的导线就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以应该能分辨出哪些是假线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 必须要想其它办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能分辨出来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要以极微小的动作在摇摆中将线切断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人类所能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确谨慎是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有时间限制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 情报就在你的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再怎么说也算是个军人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准备利用我这个情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫生纸还有剩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之在毕业前要好好的玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是校规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个笨蛋教师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无忧无虑的小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才讨厌学校这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢 接下来他准备了什么陷阱呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛应该是在监视娜娜莉的摄像机的信号接收处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到居然会是在学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经叫朱雀不要行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我所剩下的手段恐怕只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 偷腥的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不带武器也没有策略 炸弹也就这么放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团 和 刚才的朋友 都没有使用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有心情和你废话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备好了吧 最后的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来做个了结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你擅长的项目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是久违了啊 这样的悠闲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从来到AREA-11之后 预料之外的事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在做办公室的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是变胖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇姐真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇姐 你不觉得这个庭院很像玛丽安娜皇妃的离宫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说起来是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是克洛维斯皇兄的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他意外地很喜欢那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明总是和那里的鲁鲁修吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是把他当成劲敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可是比自己小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在皇兄留下的画里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鲁鲁修他们的画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽快平定这个AREA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 实在是太对不起克洛维斯以及鲁鲁修和娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是他们兄妹3人生命凋谢的天地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个天平 既是炸弹的引爆装置也是解除装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将要放上的是 双方被吃掉的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个指针完全偏向我这边的话 炸弹就会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全偏向你那边的话 炸弹就会解除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 如果你赢了 你妹妹就能获救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恶趣味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪会被C.C.抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑衅是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心里想的 我可是全都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是那种能让脑子里一片空白的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心总有一个注视着自己行动、作为批评家的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有冷眼看待这个批评家的另一个自我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你想多少花招 我的胜利都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时进行7种思考 想要迷惑我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我的Geass完全锁定在你一人身上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看穿哪一个是真的 可是很容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 最后的策略也不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为小看我 你妹妹的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经毫无办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想利用其他人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要娜娜莉还是人质…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 时间就快没了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去妹妹的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 那一手可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够了吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放过娜娜莉吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我… 是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于让我听到你发自内心深处承认失败的声音了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉真棒!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 来看看被炸成四分五裂是什么样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我的意识集中…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亚军准尉枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在以涉嫌扰乱治安的罪名拘捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把炸弹解除了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 居然配合摇摆的速度与节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要切断哪条线 鲁鲁修已经告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的指示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有听到惨叫声就突入的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛 这样就将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修 难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给自己施加Geass 让自己忘记了指示过朱雀的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是坚信我的心声为绝对正确情报的你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 为了解读我的多重思考而缩小Geass范围成了你的败笔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这家伙失败了 你准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 这是不相信朱雀就不能采用的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子小姐 已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样就赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开 你这个杀父凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在7年前杀死了自己的亲生父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为只要阻止了决心彻底抗战的父亲就能结束战争?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小孩子的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上你只不过是个杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 没有暴露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了周围的大人全替你说了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 枢木首相以自杀来劝解军部的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥天大谎 全都是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谎言…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那么做的话 日本就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还打算狡辩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个一心求死的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拯救别人?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拯救的是你自己的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个理由 所以你自己期望死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才总是将自己逼入死地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的善意只不过是为求自我满足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个想要得到惩罚的撒娇小鬼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我住口!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经喜欢过你的  毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走一步去等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在『C的世界』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.62,0:22:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.66,0:23:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是没有向毛问出关于契约的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会以这样的方式再会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:23:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前 他就想向我传达了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 要是我能好好面对的话
